@startuml
actor Admin as A
participant "Tahkik Dashboard" as Dash
database "Supabase DB" as DB

A -> Dash : Open User Management
Dash -> DB : Fetch Users List
DB --> Dash : Return Users
A -> Dash : Search or Filter Users
Dash -> Dash : Filter List
A -> Dash : View User Details
Dash -> DB : Fetch User Profile & Stats
DB --> Dash : Return Details
A -> Dash : Suspend / Activate User Account
Dash -> DB : Update User Status
DB --> Dash : Confirmation
Dash --> A : Show Success Message
@enduml
